:: Public Holidays
"New Year’s Day"                        public cultural on 1.1
"Revolution Day"                        public cultural on 12.1.
"Karume Day"                            public cultural on 7.4.
"Good Friday"                           public religious on easter minus 2 days
"Easter Monday"                         public religious on easter plus 1 days
"Union Day"                             public cultural on 26.4.
"International Worker’s Day"            public cultural on 1.5.
"Saba Saba Day"                         public cultural on 7.7.
"Peasant’s Day"                         public cultural on 8.8.
"Nyerere Day"                           public cultural on 14.10.
"Independence and Republic Day"         public cultural on 9.12.
"Christmas Day"                         public religious on 25.12.
"Boxing Day"                            public religious on 26.12.
"Maulidi Day"                           public religious on hijri rabialawal 12
"Id-ul-Fitr"                            public religious on hijri shawwal 1
"Id-ul-Fitr"                            public religious on hijri shawwal 2
"Id-el-Haj"                             public religious on hijri thualhijjah 10

